                <head>203. Editorial Note</head>
                <p>An Interagency Intelligence Memorandum, June 21, 1974, entitled “The Likelihood
                    of Conflict Between Greece and Turkey” examined the two nations’ conflicting
                    claims to rights over possible oil reserves in the Aegean Sea and the resulting
                    increased tensions. See <ref target="#d15">Document 15</ref>.</p>
            </div>
